Package arcade.util

Class Parser.Command

java.lang.Object
arcade.util.Parser.Command
Enclosing class:
Parser
private static class Parser.Command
extends java.lang.Object
Container class for arguments of a command.

A Command object is created for each command defined from parsing command.xml.
